===Pronunciation===
*καρδία / kardia / kar-dee'-ah
*Prolonged from a primary κάρ kar (Latin cor, “heart”); the heart, that is, (figuratively) the thoughts or feelings (mind); also (by analogy) the middle: - (+ broken-) [[heart]] (-ed).